  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  originalLanguage: en
  translationSets:
  - counter: 35
    languageCode: en
    translations:
    - id: 0
      language: en
      text: Druid
    - id: 1
      language: en
      text: Hi!
    - id: 2
      language: en
      text: Norfaren
    - id: 3
      language: en
      text: Did you finished?
    - id: 4
      language: en
      text: aa
    - id: 5
      language: en
      text: ttt
    - id: 6
      language: en
      text: ww
    - id: 7
      language: en
      text: fff
    - id: 8
      language: en
      text: "Musisz znale\u017A\u0107 zio\u0142a!"
    - id: 9
      language: en
      text: "Super, ale masz za ma\u0142o zi\xF3l."
    - id: 10
      language: en
      text: Udalo sie!!
    - id: 11
      language: en
      text: "Dzi\u0119ki za pomoc moj ty bohaterze!!"
    - id: 12
      language: en
      text: "Musisz znale\u017A\u0107 zio\u0142a! Przynajmniej 8!"
    - id: 13
      language: en
      text: Test
    - id: 14
      language: en
      text: fffff
    - id: 15
      language: en
      text: A
    - id: 16
      language: en
      text: B
    - id: 17
      language: en
      text: aaa
    - id: 18
      language: en
      text: Hi! How are you?
    - id: 19
      language: en
      text: You already killed forest demon? Great!
    - id: 20
      language: en
      text: Go to the south, there is demon in forest who poisoned many trees. He
        also can be responsible for people who can't wake up. Do what you have to
        do.
    - id: 21
      language: en
      text: Go to the south, there is demon in forest who has poisoned many trees.
        He also can be responsible for people who can't wake up. Do what you have
        to do.
    - id: 22
      language: en
      text: You made it! Give potion to Kaelen and wake him up!
    - id: 23
      language: en
      text: You have to find <
    - id: 24
      language: en
      text: 'You have to find Awakening herbs, it should be in somewhere in forest.
        I need 8 plants to prepare awakening potion. '
    - id: 25
      language: en
      text: Thanks for help!
    - id: 26
      language: en
      text: Go to Kaelen and ask him about his dreams.
    - id: 27
      language: en
      text: 'He was locked in his sleep. '
    - id: 28
      language: en
      text: To find out exactly what was going on there, it would be best to fall
        asleep myself, but I can't do that.
    - id: 29
      language: en
      text: But you, you have a patron, right? Maybe you could try?
    - id: 30
      language: en
      text: Come back in the next patch. Then we'll try to lock you in a dream. And
        maybe the druid grove will be more... druidic.
    - id: 31
      language: en
      text: Player
    - id: 32
      language: en
      text: Of course, I came to town to solve this mystery.
    - id: 33
      language: en
      text: Great! To find a way to lock you in your sleep, I need a way... Hmmm...
    - id: 34
      language: en
      text: Come back in the next patch. I should have found a way by then.
